 crime from the inside: Internal control and cyber crime prevention. The 2nd Annual Meeting of Asian Criminological Society.  India: Asian Criminology Society and University of Matras. (with Lennon Chang)2009●公民社會的價值維度：以各國對性工作者民意取向為例。兩岸四地政治文化與公民社會國際研討會。澳門：澳門大學與澳門社會學會。（與曹立群、侯崇文合著）2008●Adolescent Internet Mimicry and False Signals. Family, Children and Youth International Conference. HK: Hong Kong City University.●Developing public safety and crime indicators. A case-study of Taiwan. 2008 Annual Meeting of American Society of Criminology. St. Louis, MI: American Society of Criminology. (with B. Hebenton).2007●斷續之間：台灣犯罪學發展。2007年中國社會的犯罪、法律與司法─全球化挑戰及本土回應研討會。香港：香港中文大學。●National Traditions in Criminology: Issues of Method.  2007 Annual Meeting of Law and Society Association。（with B. Hebenton）German: Berlin.2005  ●In search of criminological tradition: the development of criminology in Taiwan (with B. Hebenton) 2005 Annual Meeting of American Society of Criminology。 Canada: Toronto. 2002●台灣的少年犯罪問題與對策。澳門青少年偏差行為研討會。澳門：澳門青少年犯罪研究學會暨澳門理工學院。●台灣當前貪污犯罪現況、成因與防制對策。倡導公務員廉潔守法研討會。澳門；廉政公署。（與陳隆榮等合著）2000●Reintegrative Shame and its moral deterrent effects on deviant behavior in Taiwan and US. 2000 Annual American Society of Criminology Conference. (with X. Deng). CA: San Francisco.●Measuing self-control at a very young age. 2000 Annual American Society of Criminology Conference. (with Bu Huang). CA: San Francisco.1999●青少年犯罪的空間模式與治理對策，兩岸四地青少年違法及藥物濫用防治對策學術研討會，澳門：青少年犯罪學會。��1994●The Deterrence Effect of Social Control on Delinquency in a Consensus-Oriented Culture. 1994 Annual American Society of Criminology. FL: Miami.1993●Violent Crime from Socio-Economic Polarization: A Case Study in Taiwan from 1964 to 1992, 1993 Annual American Society of Criminology. AZ: Phoenix.1992●Adolescent Substance Use: Power, Money, Friends and Drugs, 1992 Annual Academy of Criminal Justice Science.  PA: Pittsburgh. (with X. Deng)●The Causal Effects of Class and Family Structure on Adolescent Stealing Behavior," 1